parameters.name: 町・村っぽい感じ（夜っぽい）

parameters:
\n<Roselitte>"It's dangerous to travel at night, so let's camp here
tonight. We need to get ready before it gets dark."

\n<Ameria>"...No, it's nothing! I'll go gather some firewood, lots of
it!"
\n<Ameria>"Lyric, help me out. I can't carry a lot by myself."
\n<Roselitte>"...What's the matter? You seem a bit off."

\n<Lyric>"Who knows? Maybe she just likes campfires. Wants to burn a
lot of wood or something."
\n<Ameria's voice>"Lyric, hurry up! It's getting dark!"
\n<Lyric>"Ah... oh- I see. That's what it is."

\n<Lyric>"Mmm, well, you'll find out soon enough. Don't worry about
it, just prepare the meal. I'll quickly hunt something like
a deer or a rabbit. I'm getting hungry."

\n<Roselitte>"'Quickly' isn't as easy as you make it sound.... But
alright, I understand. Let me know immediately if anything
happens."
\n<Lyric>"Ah- enough, you're loud! I said I'm coming!"
